transcript:
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Bhaiya aapne apna ticket fir se open kar diya tha V2 meet wala.
Executive: Ye galti se open ho gaya bhaiya.
Customer: Galti se open ho gaya hai.
Executive: Theek hai rukiye main close kara de raha hun.
Customer: Theek hai.
Executive: Thoda line pe rahiye aap.
Executive: Theek hai main band kara raha hun na, band kara ke aapko call kar raha hun, ek minute rukiye.
Customer: Ji okay.
summary:
